snippet.title: AFTER FRIGHT - All Levels - Full Gameplay
snippet.description:
After Fright New Mobile Gameplay. Full Game Walkthrough. After the incident, the owners of the horror attraction that suffered from the fire made a decision to auction off the remaining items that were spared from the incident. During the process of organizing the auction, they reached out to a storage facility to house the salvaged items until the auction day. You play the role of David, the night security guard assigned to the warehouse, responsible for ensuring the security of the premises throughout the night. Or perhaps, attempting to keep yourself safe? You only have three attempts!🎈🎈🎈

Download Link 👇👇
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ERabbitGames.AfterFright
